original_title: Feng Shui: The Art of Creating Harmony & Balance in Your Home - A Day at the Spa Collection
overview: With the aim of creating harmony and balance, Feng Shui can help regain control and calmness over the everyday stresses. You will learn to achieve a more harmonious living environment by applying some simple and inexpensive Feng-Shui methods.
title: Feng Shui: The Art of Creating Harmony & Balance in Your Home - A Day at the Spa Collection
